Removed Threading from Video File Processing & Added README.md Template

A README.md template has been added. Everyone in the 2XStudy team, use this template to construct the final README.md file for the master branch.

A Note About Threading:
After a number of thorough testing, threading does NOT improve the runtime of video generation. In fact, if anything, threading seems to SLOW down the operation by a bit.

FINAL COMMIT

This is the final commit with the abridging video processing code. You are now free to combine this code with other back-end and front-end processes.
